  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/ee0be886a438cc44432bcfd11692464d.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><strong>Welcome to Fable Hospital!</strong> Enter a world of hospital management like you've never seen before. In this hilarious and satirical medieval simulation, you'll run your own hospital filled with eccentric characters, implausible diseases, and unique challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/b1ed2bae80f2348170792cb0dca9c4e8.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=89 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/f6804afbdc004f4311074422282b036b.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Manage your medieval hospital and ensure it runs like a well-oiled machine, or at least well enough for patients to survive… most of the time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/54a8c2a1348c09cc2f0f1236e66548bb.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/54a8c2a1348c09cc2f0f1236e66548bb.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/54a8c2a1348c09cc2f0f1236e66548bb.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/f673a05329347afb5a1a4b93cc092303.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Recruit and manage a cast of colorful characters, from the sinister Plague Doctor to the absent-minded Mad Engineer. Each employee has their own set of skills and... quirks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/2790120ae23f18b0f4ef5c356e44e4e8.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/2790120ae23f18b0f4ef5c356e44e4e8.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/2790120ae23f18b0f4ef5c356e44e4e8.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/acaebf919bbf16fd0942db0279d9ce37.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Treat patients with diseases that defy all logic, from \"Lycanthropy\" to \"Unicorn Syndrome.\" Each diagnosis is more absurd than the last!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/4dfad0584d7c805c5cd06eecea909c6d.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/4dfad0584d7c805c5cd06eecea909c6d.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/4dfad0584d7c805c5cd06eecea909c6d.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/23dfcaf0c1c63edba423c2cee1631dea.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Step outside the hospital and venture into the countryside to gather herbs, minerals, and other essential resources. Your hospital won't stock itself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/9a003dcfc0c3367dd185b1da0422a3d7.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/9a003dcfc0c3367dd185b1da0422a3d7.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/9a003dcfc0c3367dd185b1da0422a3d7.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/3023b2917403a7b83947a42b3892baa6.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Use alchemy and magic to research new cures and technologies. Unlock upgrades that make your hospital more efficient and hopefully less prone to fires.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/0eec68437640f3d8d9bad32d17fd85ca.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/0eec68437640f3d8d9bad32d17fd85ca.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/0eec68437640f3d8d9bad32d17fd85ca.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/e7db7e5dfe9724c94022daa804235f52.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Enjoy dialogues and situations filled with satirical humor. From employees who prefer to have a beer instead of working, to nuns who secretly adore parties, every moment is full of laughs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/09a8b8ac1a85fcfb372408a01516da7b.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/09a8b8ac1a85fcfb372408a01516da7b.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/09a8b8ac1a85fcfb372408a01516da7b.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/6ff345597bca7d8f05abd238546371cc.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>With detailed graphics and an art style that captures the essence of the medieval era, Fable Hospital is a visual delight that complements its clever gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/bc600677bd9289680c90983ca1d542fe.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/bc600677bd9289680c90983ca1d542fe.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/bc600677bd9289680c90983ca1d542fe.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/a2c401e7f12c26b927e398da36b71fe8.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br>In Fable Hospital, each day brings new challenges and surprises. Can you manage the chaos of a medieval hospital and keep your patients alive? Or will you find yourself caught in a sea of laughs and disasters?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/3fdae7d65bfed274b537abde324a91ab.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/166f882d4564c6c97b044402a66f0ee3.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=71 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/ee0be886a438cc44432bcfd11692464d.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><strong>Welcome to Fable Hospital!</strong> Enter a world of hospital management like you've never seen before. In this hilarious and satirical medieval simulation, you'll run your own hospital filled with eccentric characters, implausible diseases, and unique challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/b1ed2bae80f2348170792cb0dca9c4e8.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=89 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/f6804afbdc004f4311074422282b036b.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Manage your medieval hospital and ensure it runs like a well-oiled machine, or at least well enough for patients to survive… most of the time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/54a8c2a1348c09cc2f0f1236e66548bb.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/54a8c2a1348c09cc2f0f1236e66548bb.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/54a8c2a1348c09cc2f0f1236e66548bb.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/f673a05329347afb5a1a4b93cc092303.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Recruit and manage a cast of colorful characters, from the sinister Plague Doctor to the absent-minded Mad Engineer. Each employee has their own set of skills and... quirks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/2790120ae23f18b0f4ef5c356e44e4e8.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/2790120ae23f18b0f4ef5c356e44e4e8.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/2790120ae23f18b0f4ef5c356e44e4e8.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/acaebf919bbf16fd0942db0279d9ce37.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Treat patients with diseases that defy all logic, from \"Lycanthropy\" to \"Unicorn Syndrome.\" Each diagnosis is more absurd than the last!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/4dfad0584d7c805c5cd06eecea909c6d.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/4dfad0584d7c805c5cd06eecea909c6d.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/4dfad0584d7c805c5cd06eecea909c6d.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/23dfcaf0c1c63edba423c2cee1631dea.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Step outside the hospital and venture into the countryside to gather herbs, minerals, and other essential resources. Your hospital won't stock itself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/9a003dcfc0c3367dd185b1da0422a3d7.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/9a003dcfc0c3367dd185b1da0422a3d7.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/9a003dcfc0c3367dd185b1da0422a3d7.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/3023b2917403a7b83947a42b3892baa6.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Use alchemy and magic to research new cures and technologies. Unlock upgrades that make your hospital more efficient and hopefully less prone to fires.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/0eec68437640f3d8d9bad32d17fd85ca.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/0eec68437640f3d8d9bad32d17fd85ca.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/0eec68437640f3d8d9bad32d17fd85ca.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/e7db7e5dfe9724c94022daa804235f52.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Enjoy dialogues and situations filled with satirical humor. From employees who prefer to have a beer instead of working, to nuns who secretly adore parties, every moment is full of laughs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/09a8b8ac1a85fcfb372408a01516da7b.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/09a8b8ac1a85fcfb372408a01516da7b.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/09a8b8ac1a85fcfb372408a01516da7b.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/6ff345597bca7d8f05abd238546371cc.webp?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>With detailed graphics and an art style that captures the essence of the medieval era, Fable Hospital is a visual delight that complements its clever gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/bc600677bd9289680c90983ca1d542fe.poster.avif?t=1748530564\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/bc600677bd9289680c90983ca1d542fe.webm?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/bc600677bd9289680c90983ca1d542fe.mp4?t=1748530564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/a2c401e7f12c26b927e398da36b71fe8.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br>In Fable Hospital, each day brings new challenges and surprises. Can you manage the chaos of a medieval hospital and keep your patients alive? Or will you find yourself caught in a sea of laughs and disasters?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/3fdae7d65bfed274b537abde324a91ab.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726060/extras/166f882d4564c6c97b044402a66f0ee3.avif?t=1748530564\" width=600 height=71 /></span>",
